		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Independently from the actual historic situation, I don't think the anime is really aware of the existence of any other churches besides the Catholic one, as it's the case in so many movies.<br />So, the bishop and his gang are not intended to represent struggles between the various denominations. The other priest that was shown might not be part of the power hungry gang of priests, but they all still belong to the same church.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
